Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.49,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:90653,94490}{\i1}Even though the local performances\Nfit Nozomi's dreams very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.57,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:94490,97577}{\i1}they gave her only pain and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:42.45,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:97577,102457}{\i1}During that time, she met a trumpeter Nitta,\Nwho has lost his passion for music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:44.70,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:102457,104709}{\i1}She managed to\Nreignite that lost spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:48.58,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:104709,108588}{\i1}Meanwhile, DM Pro kept making the group\Nmove from one town to another,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.71,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:108588,110715}{\i1}to the point Nozomi had lost her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:57.01,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:110882,117013}{\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&\t(0,1500,0.4,\1c&HEBFEFF&\3c&H1C242D&\4c&H000000&)}— Episode 12 —\NDon't Cry, Dear{NOTE:第12話\\N泣くな花笠}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.77,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:129525,132779}{\i1}The trip in the Tōhoku region continued on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:17.53,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:132779,137533}{\i1}Nozomi's voice, who had\Nalways singed with great passion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:21.57,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:137533,141579}{\i1}moved the hearts of people\Nin these faraway lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:25.62,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:141579,145625}{\i1}Her popularity was steadily making her\Nbecome the center of the troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.96,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:145625,148961}{\fad(0,1000)}Great March "A New Spring"\NAll star cast!{NOTE:青春歌謡大行進\\Nオールスターキャスト豪華}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.63,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:148127,151631}{\fad(1000,0)}Straight from DM Studio based in Tōkyō\N{\fs30}Mizushima Takeshi · Hoshimura Hiromi · Mine Nozomi{NOTE:東京DMスタジオ水\\N島たけし星村ひろみ峰のぞみ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:38.76,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:155259,158763}Watch out, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.85,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:160890,163851}Whoa, awesome, what\Na big truck! Two, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:46.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:165770,166854}We're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:171109,173736}Whoa, the air's so fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:173736,175780}So peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:58.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:175780,178866}I'd like to take\Nmy mom here someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.41,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:179701,181411}Oh, my, look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.08,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:181411,184080}What is there to be so excited about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.58,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:185123,187583}I envy her happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.79,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:187583,190795}She's just a little girl,\Nnot knowing the hardships of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.80,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:191462,195800}To think we're forced to share\Nthe spotlight with a beginner like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.67,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:195800,197677}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:22.09,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:197677,202098}Don't stand like that, dreamboats.\NCome on, get your luggage off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.80,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:202098,204809}You don't want to be late\Nfor your afternoon show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.18,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:205351,207186}What afternoon show?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.43,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:207186,209439}We've barely arrived\Nand we're to sing already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.98,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:209439,211983}Things move too fast lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.61,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:211983,214610}Orders from the manager, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.40,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:214610,217405}If you have any complaints,\Ntake them to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.82,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:217405,220825}Who do you think you are?\NVery well. I'll talk to the manager myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.07,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:220825,222076}Come with me, Mizushima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.66,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:222076,224662}H-Hey, what about\Nyour luggage? Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:224662,226330}I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.42,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:230126,232420}Wow, she can handle it pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:00.80,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:236591,240803}I know! That girl is the singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.97,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:240803,242972}The one you saw\Nin the posters earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.05,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:242972,244056}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.39,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:244056,246392}She's one pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.26,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:246392,248269}She's here to sing for us!\NI'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.06,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:249896,252064}Grandma! Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.44,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:253858,255443}Are you okay, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:256235,257945}I'm terribly sorry.\NAre you okay, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.40,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:257945,259405}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:262325,264452}I'm so sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.53,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:264452,266537}Don't worry about it, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:266537,267705}I'm sorry, I really am—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.50,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:267705,270500}You can't do anything\Non an empty stomach, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:270958,272502}Y-You're perfectly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:37.34,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:273044,277340}Good that I had food with me.\NHere, you can have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:277340,279884}Thank you very much, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:279884,281010}I'm very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.34,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:284514,286349}Is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:286933,288643}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.02,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:289811,292021}Even singers get hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.35,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:292021,293356}Oh, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.36,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:299695,302365}Why the long face?\NYou don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:303991,306744}It's just that you prepare it like my mom.\NIt reminds me of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.37,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:306744,309372}You came here from Tōkyō, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:310206,311374}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:315711,316921}I look stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.59,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:317421,320591}You came on purpose from Tōkyō\Nto sing in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:320591,322385}Yes. I'm still just a beginner, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.88,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:322385,324887}I, err… I want to hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:29.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:325721,329767}Sure. I have a younger brother\Nwho is around your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.97,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:329767,331978}Hey, Mine!\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:331978,333396}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:336983,338442}Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:338442,340027}Please come to our concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:40.90,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:340027,340903}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:340903,343364}I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:51.41,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:346450,351414}Anyway, we're not the only ones tired.\NThe band, Uragata-san as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:57.58,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:353666,357587}Then there's Nozomi with her sore throat.\NYou want a little break as well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.67,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:357587,359672}Yes. But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:359672,361382}But I'll get on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:07.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:363467,367388}I promised to that boy and his grandma\Nthat I'll be there. I have to give my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.14,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:368306,370141}That's great, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.72,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:370141,373728}It's no wonder why our company's\Npresident likes her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:18.39,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:373728,378399}If you're calling yourselves professionals,\Nyou have a lot to learn from this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.73,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:378399,379734}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:24.40,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:379734,384405}If she's so good, she can do the concert all alone.\NAnyway, I have a cold and must rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.07,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:384405,386073}I'll be at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.70,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:386782,388701}Frankly, she starts to annoy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.07,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:388701,391078}The more popular,\Nthe more they get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:51.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:406260,411223}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Long, long life to you,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:目出度目出度の }
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:57.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:411223,417730}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  O' great young pine  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:若松様よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:01.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:417730,421859}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  To you and your branches  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:枝も}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:12.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:421859,432328}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Be it prosperous and leafy  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:栄えて葉も茂る}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:17.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:432328,437333}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Back in my hometown  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:わしがお国で}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:23.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:437333,443965}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  our pride are  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:自慢なものは}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:28.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:443965,448177}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  eggplants,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:茄子と}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:38.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:448177,458688}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  cucumbers and the Gasa Dance  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:胡瓜と笠踊}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.69,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:459063,461691}Hey, Grandma?\NWhere are you going? Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.61,Default,Grandson,0,0,0,,{TIME:463067,465611}Wait! Stop!\NYou're embarrassing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:49.61,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:465611,469615}Go back to your seat!\NLet grandma have a little fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:52.20,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:469615,472201}What do you mean, embarrassing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.28,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:472451,476288}What the heck is she doing?\NDo something about that wicked old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:56.99,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:476288,476998}Y-Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.96,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:477123,480960}Go for it, grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.96,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:486465,489969}Such smooth moves! What a babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.72,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:495099,497727}Encore! Encore, grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.97,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:498102,499979}That was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.77,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:502523,505776}– Oh, they like it. Thank heavens.\N– You worry too much, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:31.28,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:506068,511282}Thank you. Thanks to you, for a moment\NI forgot I'm 60 years old and felt young again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:35.53,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:511282,515536}Even my rheumatism\Nhas disappeared. Haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:516370,518080}Ma'am…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:518080,519999}I hope you live another 60 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.00,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:519999,522001}You too, live long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.21,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,{TIME:522001,525212}And don't carry\Nall those boxes by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:532803,534680}I'm back, Hoshimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:534680,536182}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:59.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:536182,539477}When you have cold, it's better\Nto rest and take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:02.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:539477,542688}Here, have some fruit.\NI got it from one of our fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:07.98,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:542688,547985}Hmph. I haven't fallen so low\Nto accept second hand gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:547985,551822}No, that's not what I meant to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:16.36,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:552782,556368}You got sore throat and yet\Nyou get on stage and sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.95,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:556368,559955}You're willing to do anything\Nto steal my place, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:560539,562583}Steal your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:562583,564085}I'd never want such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.75,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:564085,566754}It's all right.\NYou don't have to pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.84,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:566754,569840}I'd do the same if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:32.80,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:569840,572802}It's natural for anyone\Nwho aims for stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:37.64,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:572802,577640}It's just that after taking so much care\Nof your throat, it doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:41.01,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:577640,581018}I thought we were on the same boat,\Nbut I was clearly wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:581018,583020}I'm sorry, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.31,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:583020,585314}"But"? But what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:585314,588567}There are people who are happy\Nto listen to my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:588567,589819}That's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:589819,591654}I have no choice but to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.78,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:591654,594782}I see that you're convinced\Nyou're a very good singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:10:00.20,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:594782,600204}Very well. I don't mean to waste any more time\Nassociating with you. It's just useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:09.79,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:605751,609797}W-What did you say? Hoshimura\Ndoesn't want to get on stage tonight at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.38,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:609797,611382}What a prima donna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.25,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:611382,613259}Throw her out!\NLeave her nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.51,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:613259,615511}I'm so done listening\Nto her constant pouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.88,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:615511,616887}Strip her naked!\NKick her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:17.97,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:616887,617972}Y-Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:619723,621183}Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:621183,623310}Don't fire Hoshimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:623310,625604}That's terrible.\NPlease don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:625604,626564}If…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:30.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:626564,630484}If it's okay with, you, I can go on stage\Ntonight in Hoshimura-san's stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.77,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:630484,632778}Oh, you, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:36.11,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:632778,636115}If you could replace her,\Nit would be a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.61,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:636115,637616}Very well, it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.16,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:637616,640161}Here. It's Hoshimura's repertoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.53,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:640828,642538}Learn it by heart for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.16,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:642538,645166}– I know you'll be fine.\N– Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:51.83,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:647918,651839}Think it over. Do you seriously\Nwant to destroy your throat even further?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.05,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:653132,656051}I know how you feel.\NYou only want to help Hoshimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.68,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:656051,659680}But that's not something\Nyou should sacrifice yourself for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:659680,661140}That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:04.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:661140,664393}I want to try and find out\Nhow far I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.10,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:664393,667104}That's it. That's the charm\Nof our young Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.81,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:667104,668814}Soon it's time for Hoshimura's entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:13.23,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:668814,673235}You will become famous,\Nso play your cards well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:18.36,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:673235,678365}If things go well, we might be able to double\Nor even triple the amount on your contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.10,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:702723,705100}Let's go back inside.\NIt's past midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:705100,708020}I want to learn how to sing as well\Nas Hoshimura-san does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.06,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:708020,711065}If you're not careful,\Nyou won't have any future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.44,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:715152,717446}See? That's what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.61,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:717446,719615}I'm in love with your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.82,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:719615,722826}It's a sensational voice\Nof enormous potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.53,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:722826,725537}If you take care of it,\Nyou'll become famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:10.08,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:725537,730084}This is why I can't stand how that bastard\Nkeeps you working like a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.17,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:730626,733170}What was that?\NIt was inside. Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.72,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:744265,745724}That's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.10,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:746517,748102}Now it's all useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:32.77,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:748102,752773}What are we going to do tomorrow\Nwithout any microphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:752773,754858}{\i1}Who could've done such thing?
Comment: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:37.44,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:757444,757444}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.98,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:757444,759989}{\fad(0,1000)}Mizushima Takeshi\NMine Nozomi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.61,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:759154,761615}Mine Nozomi, a "top star", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:05.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:779300,785472}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm a woman, so I love  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:女ですもの 恋をする}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:11.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:785472,791562}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm a woman, so I dream  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:女ですもの 夢に酔う}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:17.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:791562,797526}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm a woman, so…  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:女ですもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:23.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:797526,803782}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm all alone  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:ただ一人}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:34.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:803782,814376}{\an8\fad(0,2000)\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm a woman, so I keep going on  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:女ですもの生きて行く}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.55,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:784388,786557}What do you think?\NShe's great, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.43,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:786557,789435}You can hear her perfectly\Neven without the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.85,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:789435,791854}That just means\Nshe has to try all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:16.27,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:791854,796275}If she continues like that,\Nshe'll be mute in less than half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.11,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:798610,800112}Excuse me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.87,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:804658,807870}What are you doing here?\NYou should be resting in a bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.91,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:807870,810914}My cold wasn't\Nvery serious to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.41,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:810914,813417}I just pulled wool over his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:36.21,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:813417,816211}We can't always be\Nunder the manager's thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.88,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:816211,818881}What!? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:43.63,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:818881,823635}Look over there. Because of your stupid stunt,\NNozomi's ruining her throat on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.38,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:824845,827389}It's all the better if she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.80,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:827389,830809}That cocky kid, trying to steal\Nthe popularity from me. It's my payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:54.43,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:830809,834438}By the way, it was me\Nwho destroyed the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.27,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:834438,836273}Hoshimura! It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.77,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:836273,838776}Mizushima-san.\NYou just can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:02.23,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:838776,842237}You don't know how it feels\Nwhen she sings my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.90,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:842237,844907}I do, better than you think.\NBut you're making a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:08.45,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:844907,848452}The manager was about to get you fired,\Nbut she begged him not to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.45,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:849495,850454}Fire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.28,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:850913,852289}Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:17.16,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:852289,857169}He got mad when he found out you didn't\Nwant to sing, and luckily for you, she stepped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.12,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:857169,859129}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.54,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:859129,860547}Damn right I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:26.30,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:860547,866303}Why else do you think she risks losing\Nher voice, singing other people's songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:14:00.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:834688,840903}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I want to trust you alone  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたひとりに すがりたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:07.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:840903,847034}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I want to depend on you alone  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたひとりに 甘えたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:19.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:847034,859296}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I want to live with you alone  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたひとりに この命}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:29.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:859296,869973}{\an8\fad(0,2000)\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I want to live for you alone  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたひとりに ささげたい }
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:890786,893288}Ladies and gentlemen,\Nsorry for the lack of microphone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:56.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:893288,896692}Though I think it's difficult to hear,\NI'll try my best to sing nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:12.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:901522,912241}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  When you choose the way of love,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  everything becomes right  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:人は愛に生き　平和に生きる}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:22.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:912241,922709}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  What was your happiness,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  becomes everyone's  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:一人の幸せは　みんなの幸せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:27.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:922709,927256}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Cherish your dreams,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:夢は大切に　}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:32.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:927256,932261}{\an8\fnArial\fad(0,2000)}♪{\fn}  and connect…{NOTE:こころとこころが}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:12.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:911031,912574}{\i1}I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:15.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:912574,915077}{\i1}I won't lose to this pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:19.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:915077,919123}{\i1}I'll sing till the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:36.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:934888,936140}{\i1}My voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:936140,938767}{\i1}My voice… won't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:938767,940394}{\i1}My voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:941854,943522}{\i1}It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.98,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:945274,946984}– What's wrong?\N– What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.69,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:946984,948694}Curtain, curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:54.40,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:950612,954408}Nozomi-chan, forgive me.\NI've completely misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:58.20,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:954408,958203}Listen, Mine-kun. Hoshimura-san\Nwill take over now. You can rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:960122,961915}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:10.09,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:965836,970090}Oh, Mr. President?\NMine has collapsed on stage…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:13.88,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:970090,973886}She's got a sore throat. The local doctor\Nsays she needs to rest for at least ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:16.55,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:973886,976555}What should we do?\NShall we go back to Tōkyō?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.34,Default,DM president,0,0,0,,{TIME:976555,978348}{\i1}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:21.39,Default,DM president,0,0,0,,{TIME:978348,981393}{\i1}The tour is scheduled\Nto run 5 or 6 more shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.64,Default,DM president,0,0,0,,{TIME:981393,983645}{\i1}Plus our contract with\NMine Nozomi is just a phony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.60,Default,DM president,0,0,0,,{TIME:983645,986607}{\i1}Just cancel it.\NWhy do you even call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:29.44,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:986607,989443}All right, then.\NI'll let her continue till the last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.27,Default,DM president,0,0,0,,{TIME:989443,991278}{\i1}Naturally you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:32.94,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:991278,992946}I-I understand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:35.94,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:992946,995949}I'll see to get the most out of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.07,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:997910,1000078}What are you doing?!\NI have a task for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009046,1010881}{\i1}Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010881,1013967}{\i1}I really feel like a canary\Nthat can no longer sing a single note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:57.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013967,1017054}{\i1}But in 10 days…\NI'll be better in 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:17:00.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017054,1020098}{\i1}I bet you're struggling\Nin that foreign country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:02.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020098,1022893}{\i1}When I think of it,\NI can find the strength to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:04.10,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023310,1024102}Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.40,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027022,1030400}I'm really sorry.\NForgive me for being so petty before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.40,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030400,1033403}How can I ever apologize to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:16.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033862,1036490}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036490,1038659}Actually, I'm thankful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:21.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038659,1041245}I came to know what my limits are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.08,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041995,1045082}Nozomi-chan, here…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:28.25,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045082,1048252}It's the least I can do for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:31.79,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048252,1051797}It's not much, but it should be enough\Nto safely get you back to Tōkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:34.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051797,1054883}Thank you, but I'm not\Ngoing back to Tōkyō yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054883,1056843}Or rather, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:38.55,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056843,1058553}You're thinking about your contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:43.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058553,1063016}Yes. I need that money very much,\Nso I have to work for it till I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:46.43,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063016,1066436}I'm sorry, but haven't you\Nnoticed you're still being fooled?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:47.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066436,1067938}Fooled?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.94,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067938,1070941}Yes. It's a contract,\Nbut it's just an empty promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.40,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070941,1073402}Even if you do get paid,\Nit'll be next to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.61,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073402,1075612}It's been like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:58.36,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075612,1078365}Anyway, that's not\Nthe place for you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:01.61,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078365,1081618}You must've had your own suspicions.\NThey're gangsters scamming people left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.66,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081618,1083662}You can't imagine what else\Nthey might be capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:06.03,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083662,1086039}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:07.95,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086039,1087958}It's just like Hoshimura-kun says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:12.37,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087958,1092379}Mine-kun. Don't take it the wrong way,\Nbut I think it's best for you to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.63,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092379,1094631}It might come off as intrusive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:18.51,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094631,1098510}but I'd like you to think of it\Nas help from your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:22.34,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098510,1102347}We've even arranged your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:33.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110605,1113358}Thank you.\NI'm going back to Tōkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.61,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114109,1115610}Good call. It's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.36,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115610,1118363}I think you will make it in time\Nfor the last train.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:41.61,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118363,1121616}Take care of your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:45.37,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121616,1125370}I'm looking forward to the day\Nyou stand in the Tōkyō's limelight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:50.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127456,1130208}I will never forgive\Nabout the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130208,1131376}All right then, good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:56.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134588,1136506}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.09,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136506,1139092}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148268,1149644}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:14.23,Default,DM worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149644,1154232}If you don't make it to our next show,\Nit'll become a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:16.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154649,1156109}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156109,1157235}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:27.57,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1165577,1167579}{\an2}DM Productions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:40.13,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167829,1180133}Whew, this is the place.\NNo mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.62,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170624,1173627}Finally I've caught up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.54,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175379,1177547}Hey, hey, hey, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.13,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177547,1180133}What are you doing\Nto this board I've finally found?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:44.42,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180675,1184429}Well, the show is over,\Nand the audience is all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.13,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184429,1186139}Huh? Over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:48.47,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186139,1188475}Yeah. You were a little bit too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.64,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188475,1190644}DM Pro sure has it rough, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:53.43,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190644,1193438}They have another show\Ntomorrow in Namioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:56.14,Default,Worker,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193438,1196149}If you hurry up,\Nyou may get there in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:05.03,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202489,1205033}Damn, I was late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:10.03,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205575,1210038}What kind of fan am I?\NI'm no good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:17.21,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213792,1217212}{\i1}No, wait.\NI'm the Great Kumagorō.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:20.29,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217212,1220298}{\i1}What good will it do\Nif I pull back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.30,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220298,1222300}{\i1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:30.01,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228056,1230016}{\i1}Wait for me, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245615,1247576}{\i1}Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248493,1250287}{\i1}Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251037,1253457}{\i1}Kazuo. Yuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253457,1255542}{\i1}Ah, I want to see them so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255542,1257752}{\i1}I can't wait till I see their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:02.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259921,1262591}{\i1}Wait. If I can escape,\Nnow is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:16.39,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275770,1276396}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:17.52,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276396,1277522}Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:20.98,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279107,1280984}Where might you be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:24.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280984,1284529}I'm sorry, but I need\Nto go to bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:27.32,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284529,1287324}I see. Just don't get\Nany weird ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:51.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308512,1311598}{\i1}I'm so scared.\NWhat do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:53.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312641,1313725}{\i1}Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316061,1317312}{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321441,1323944}{\i1}I have to escape.\NI have to escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.17,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341753,1343171}Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:25.42,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343171,1345423}Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:27.75,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346216,1347759}Hang in there, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:29.42,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347759,1349427}Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:32.43,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349928,1352430}It's me, Nozomi-chan.\NIt's your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:38.43,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356977,1358436}Ah, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:41.64,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360021,1361648}You're awake, Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.64,0:22:43.19,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361648,1363191}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:45.86,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363191,1365860}Things must've been tough for you.\NYou don't have to worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:48.44,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365860,1368446}Your number one fan is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:56.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372784,1376204}Kuma-san… I want to go back to Tōkyo.\NI want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:59.58,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1377497,1379583}I know, I know.\NIt's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:00.91,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1379583,1380917}You want to go home, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:03.46,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1380917,1383461}Let's go back.\NTo your home in Tōkyō.
Comment: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:31.77,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1411773,1411773}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:37.89,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412515,1417896}{\i1}After Nozomi returns home with Kumagorō\Nat her side, she must face more hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:41.44,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1417896,1421441}{\i1}She needs to find\Na new way of life soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:47.94,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421441,1427948}{\i1}She gets approached by Kōda Miki,\Nwho is steadily treading on the path of stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:52.76,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427948,1432761}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"The Grass That Grows Again".
Comment: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:52.76,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432761,1432761}Ending
